THEY GOT PERMISSION TO TURN THAT

18:09.855 --> 18:11.857
SWITCH ON LAST MONTH, AND THEIR

18:11.857 --> 18:12.725
SOLAR SYSTEM IS NOW UP AND

18:12.725 --> 18:14.694
RUNNING.

