HER LATE 60s LIVING IN ARIZONA,

21:51.977 --> 21:54.580
A FASCINATING STORY.

21:54.580 --> 21:56.315
HAD A WONDERFUL CONVERSATION

21:56.315 --> 21:57.316
WITH HER ABOUT HER MOTHER ABOUT

