AND I'M THRILLED TO SEE THAT IN

22:03.355 --> 22:05.658
MANY WAYS, HER LIFE WAS EXACTLY

22:05.658 --> 22:06.725
WHAT HER MOTHER HAD HOPED FOR

22:06.725 --> 22:08.627
HER, AND SHE WENT ON TO DO MANY

22:08.627 --> 22:09.828
OF THE THINGS HER MOTHER WAS NOT

