AND WHATNOT, IT'S REALLY THE BAD

23:49.795 --> 23:51.430
ROADS OR BAD DRIVING AND A

23:51.430 --> 23:52.698
MIXTURE OF THE TWO.

23:52.698 --> 23:53.732
>> Reporter: HIS JOURNEY TOOK

23:53.732 --> 23:56.902
